CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper June 3, 1967, pg. 20, reads: "This Week's Traffic Blocker.  This inconsiderate and unlawful driver was caught be the photographer near the corners of Braddock and Homewood Aves.  Do you know him?"
TitMainTitle: Car double parked on North Homewood Avenue, with Bell Luncheonette at 531, and Goodyear P & R Tire Service in background, near intersection of Alsace Way, Homewood
